<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.5">
<l>paruvak karumuki lottu muttuṭai mākaṭa lottu</l>
<l>varuvit tiraḷtikaḻ kiṉṟa vāyiram poṉmalai yottu</l>
<l>vuruvak karuṅkuḻa lāycci tiṟattiṉa mālviṭai ceṟṟu</l>
<l>teruvil tiḷaittuva ruvāṉ cittira kūṭattuḷ ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who appeared resembling the dark clouds of the [rainy] season,</l>
<l rend="indent">resembling the pearl[-laden] vast sea,</l>
<l>Resembling a thousand golden mountains which glimmer</l>
<l rend="indent">with myriad cascades,</l>
<l>Frolicking in the street, having killed the dark bull of the herd</l>
<l>For the herdess with black-hued curls, he is the one present in Citrakūṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
